":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講經咩，打得仗，邊有正義可言<br />\n日本同泡菜俾中原呢邊剝削左近千幾年，淨係計中史書打下飛機都唔知大大小小幾多次征高麗，又要臣服你，女人家眷又要進貢俾你，南京屠殺有定冇都冇咩值得追究</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n史實要承認，即使你去日本搵返啲正常嘅歷史資料(唔係右翼出嗰堆)<br />\n唔少都有記載南京大屠殺呢件事<br />\n問題係我最唔鍾意中共一副受害者嘅嘴臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你啦嗰陣仗又唔係你打，有乜事仲要自己走撚左去由得其他人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋蘇聯嗰陣死得仲多人啦，又唔見普京而家不斷哭訴德國佬殺佢全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97593635654968d1fffd087500479b81592d7b5a","tid":36652,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c23d3350aa1452ff7076cceaf67ce12ab5a370","tid":36652,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無睇內文 淨睇標題 5毛賊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你俾我地呀？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主俾人捉去打把都黎唔切啦啦 post事實點會有錢收呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b184b895b7d4f822fd742057f24814acac307cc5","tid":36652,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"華人同香港人有種劣根性係聽人講就當真當自己發生經歷過 <br />\n<br />\n我估南京事件都係咁作大"},{"pid":"8ab5ce253e2bd1c7c406571d8cb7d85217c43e68","tid":36652,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c8126c01162c81e913c8205f483f44af313ae5","tid":36652,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4def14459a37f963a85983554ab66bc