ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"日本某班人話到無南京屠殺係假，<br />\n但支那d相片證據人數都係不盡不實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果大和民族不幸成為中華第五十七個民族，南京事件只不過係另一單嘉定三屠揚州十日長春圍城，唔會放大到今日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3348e635b162d6b06392998f8458754e5b21dd31","tid":36652,"uid":22893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人無知便無敵<br />\n<br />\n竟然可以當南京大屠殺無發生過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有讀過書讀歷史都知當年日本士兵要同返日本國民交代自己幾咁正義，<br />\n<br />\n先至強迫南京人同日軍影依輯相登日本報紙，等日本人以為自己國家幾咁偉大拯救萬民<br />\n<br />\n唔好低質到唔承認歷史事實，咁同中國政府唔認文革唔認六四無分別<br />\n<br />\n唔識既話建議去多啲博物館（香港博物館，新加坡博物館，南京大屠殺博物館）增值下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己去過南京大屠殺博物館，入面啲相、幾百副屍骨真係刻骨銘心<br />\n<br />\n利申：祟日、非五毛、反共</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解主流講既你就信，你講個啲証明全部支那開既，唔好人講咩你信咩啦on9 <br />\n<br />\n利申：五毛、祟毛、反日"},{"pid":"1840b76f26497e49adc9f3d276af1f174eb7c3b3","tid":36652,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又黎"},{"pid":"3a760d768678b9445a6cd8ea779149f2b13f3d08","tid":36652,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pF9PomUbjt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpF9PomUbjt8&d=XUpR1w18NYSoxPAPi1Vv8HvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f685960f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pF9PomUbjt8</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下呢個低俗頻道製作既節目<br />\n照片還原南京大屠殺啦<br />\n人地本土派網台，喺呢個時候都怒斥班冇人性嘅人渣日軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f11f0c6d7185ba906bd0c074d802bde75e254e3","tid":36652,"uid":16518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係唔信樓主，只係想知<br />\n點解會有咁多呀公呀婆成日走出黎話咩日本侵略個幾年好撚慘乜乜柒柒<br />\n個d係臨記？定係佢地所講嘅日本仔其實係中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話駁你，但都唔係好見有人走出嚟話文革土改果陣冇野食，唔通飢荒又假架咩？<br />\n<br />\n利申:認同巴打個問題</blockquote><br />\n要有人講冇野食，我諗你要識通靈"},{"pid":"2f35b4222b27bfd4be6a617a72078145a53714f8","tid":36652,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係唔信樓主，只係想知<br />\n點解會有咁多呀公呀婆成日走出黎話咩日本侵略個幾年好撚慘乜乜柒柒<br />\n個d係臨記？定係佢地所講嘅日本仔其實係中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本仔果時自己都物資短缺，所以比日本仔統治慘，係好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇嘢食係因為資源太少啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61312b8459c23338964fe53b1ab8619d626883b3","tid":36652,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e4ab4d2e5c4ef98d6b5f5f76c33c8daadc4f24","tid":36652,"uid":36411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"我愛劉明"},{"pid":"be2cfd3d27dcdb72cd5dee07483efaa5e453e5b1","tid":36652,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"由勝者編寫<br />\n<br />\n你相信嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}